    "section2": {
      "title": "Tradition and innovation",
      "descrizione": "The history of the Charrère family since 1750 still sees today the respect of traditions, values and environment handed down with wisdom for 6 generations. Passion, craftsmanship, love for the terroir, spirit of innovation and care for the field and cellar are the driving force behind Les Crêtes, which is dedicated to heroic viticulture in the Aosta Valley with body and soul.",
      "family": "The Charrère family",
      "rifugio": "The refuge",
      "terroir": "The Terroir"
    },
    "section3": {
      "title": "In the heart of Valle d'Aosta with the Wine Refuge, Les Crêtes opens the doors to its world",
      "descrizione": "We are waiting for you in the tasting room & Wine Shop Il Rifugio del Vino, where with a view on the vineyards, you can meet us, discover our wines and the heart of our cellar, with a dedicated experience",
      "scopri": "Book your experience"
    },
    "section4": {
      "title": "Mountain wines, the children of a heroic viticulture",
      "descrizione": "Our wines express the essence of the Valdostano terroir. They are the children of a heroic and artisanal viticulture, made of extreme and difficult conditions. Created with passion and wisdom, they are dedicated to amateurs and experts. Fresh, elegant, they tell of the mountain and the family that produces them. They are the children of small vineyards cultivated by hand and cared for in detail, to obtain healthy grapes with low yields, following both in the field and in the cellar, traditional and eco-sustainable practices to protect the environment. The annual total production is on average around 225,000 bottles."
    },
