    "section5": {
      "title1": "Sustainability",
      "descrizione": "We are committed to environmental sustainability and follow the European guidelines for phytosanitary treatments, focusing on the limited use of pesticides. Our dedication to quality and passion for the surrounding area are at the heart of our philosophy.",
      "title2": "Commitment",
      "descrizione2": "The key principle of our philosophy is to continue to follow the values of past generations, enhancing the 'Terroir' with fidelity and respect for traditions. However, our focus is always on the future of innovation that allows us to fully express the potential of the mountain wine territory of Valle d'Aosta.",
      "cta": "Discover our commitment"
    },
